metadata.name: LibertasSpectrum #1
metadata.description: "Spectrum of The Miserable World" is a collection of AI generated artworks by Libertas. This collection aims to inspire all crypto lovers and community members to reflect on the darkness, immortality and chaos in this world, and to imagine a world with hope and sympathy. Libertas Spectrum holders receive access to exclusive drops, experiences and more. We are in this journey together!
